enum tmrm_error_type_t

Many bad things could happen in the subject map sphere.

Enumerator:
TMRM_NO_ERROR  No error is produced.

TMRM_MEMORY_ERROR  Cannot allocate or reallocate a block of memory.

TMRM_STORAGE_ERROR  Error in the storage backend.
TMRM_MODEL_ERROR  Something's wrong with the ontology.
